<h1 class="title">Ryerson releases Anti-Black Racism Campus Climate Review Report</h1>
<div class="subTitle">New presidential committee announced to implement recommendations from report to confront anti-Black racism</div>

<div class="author">By: Antoinette Mercurio</div>
<div class="date">July 24, 2020</div>


</div>

	<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="dab45d73-113a-4a35-a8dd-62d41b8e2128">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/news-events/news/2020/07/abrr-event-recap.jpg" alt="Two people discussing information on a computer screen"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>The university released its Anti-Black Racism Campus Climate Review Report, outlining the experiences of Black students, faculty and staff on campus. Photo: <a href="https://unsplash.com/@nesabymakers">NESA by Makers via Unsplash<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>.</p>
</div>
						    
					
				</div>
